    "|---|------|----------|---------|\n",
    "| A | Architecture | Backbone | EfficientNet-B0 vs ResNet-50 |\n",
    "| B | Windowing | Preprocessing | 3-window stack vs single window (brain only) |\n",
    "| C | Augmentation | Data augmentation | ON vs OFF |\n",
    "| D | Normalization | Normalize stats | Dataset-specific vs ImageNet |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Required input\n",
    "- Preprocessing cache (Notebook 02 output) — `manifest.csv` + `cache/` NPY arrays\n",
    "- **No pre-trained weights needed** — all variants start from ImageNet init"
